Values.Value: SATA Hydraulic Bottle Jacks of high professional quality and reinforced structure are ideal for lifting automobiles/passenger cars or other high loads according to their capacity. Used and recommended by mechanical professionals and workers who seek quality and safety for their daily work without losing efficiency and practicality.
